         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility"> ¶ Melbourne bot. Garden ¶ 20/5/65 ¶ Letter marked: 'Has the remittce been returned to the Govt of Madras? 31.5.65 E.S.S.'. ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ In reply to your letter of the 15th instant ¶ Letter not found, b...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">65.05.20b</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Edward Symonds</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">65/R4024, unit 309, VPRS 1207/P000 inward registered correspondence, VA 865 Department of the Treasurer, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Melbourne bot. Garden</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">20/5/65<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter marked: 'Has the remittce been returned to the Govt of Madras? 31.5.65 <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>E.S.S.'.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In reply to your letter of the 15th instant<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found, but a draft of it is on the file: 'Dr Mueller Have you rec'd a remittance from the Madras Govt to repay this expense? 15.5.65 <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>E.S.S.'. Other minutes on the file are<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>an<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>illegible comment<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>'Ask Dr Mueller whether the […] is to understand that the money has been sent back <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>E.S.S. 27/5'. For<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>M's<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>reply<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to the latter, see M to E. Symonds, 1 June 1865.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I have the honor to inform you, that I immediately after the receipt of a remittance of the Madras Government communicated with the honorable the Chief Secretary, to learn whether the money voted by the Victorian Government should be refunded or the remittance be applied to obtaining new supplies of the tree-seeds. On learning from my honorable Chief, that the fund should be returned I have acted accordingly.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">E Symonds Esq &amp;c &amp;c &amp;c</p>
         </div>
